# SmartCart — Environment Variables
#
# No runtime secrets belong here. All credentials (store usernames/passwords,
# Resend API key) are entered via the app UI and stored in Android Keystore
# via expo-secure-store.
#
# EAS project ID is set automatically after running: eas build:configure
# EXPO_PUBLIC_EAS_PROJECT_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
